query: DELETE o1 FROM orders o1 INNER JOIN orders o2 ON o1.serviceNumber = o2.serviceNumber AND (o1.orderNumber = o2.orderNumber OR (o1.orderNumber IS NULL AND o2.orderNumber IS NULL) OR (o1.orderNumber = '' AND o2.orderNumber = '')) WHERE o1.id > o2.id;
